headline: This Aircraft Maker Tops Buy Point After Strong Deliveries
summary: Shares of Airbus climbed above a buy point Monday after reports said the airplane maker exceeded its annual delivery goal.  A rally in the defense sector also appeared to bolster Airbus stock.  Citing unnamed sources, Bloomberg said Airbus boosted deliveries in the final days of December to beat its goal.
